Description: Professional CAD application (C++/Qt6)
 Hydra CAD is a professional CAD application with Inventor-style UI,
 sketch-based modeling, assembly support, and optional eigen kernel
 for built-in geometry (eigen kernel).
 .
 Build with -DCAD_USE_EIGENER_KERN=ON for built-in geometry kernel.
